---
---

<section id="sobre" class="bg-light text-primary">
  <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row">
    <!-- Text Content -->
    <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 p-12 lg:p-24 flex items-center justify-center relative">
      <!-- Decorative Leaf SVG (simplified) -->
      <div class="absolute left-4 lg:left-12 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 opacity-20 hidden md:block">
        <svg width="120" height="200" viewBox="0 0 120 200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1">
          <path d="M60,200 C60,150 20,120 20,70 C20,40 40,20 60,10 C80,20 100,40 100,70 C100,120 60,150 60,200 Z" />
          <path d="M60,10 L60,200" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>
          <!-- Add some branching lines -->
          <path d="M60,150 C40,140 30,120 30,100" />
          <path d="M60,120 C80,110 90,90 90,70" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-md relative z-10 ml-0 md:ml-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif leading-tight mb-8">
          NATUREZA <br/>
          COM PROPÓSITO. <br/>
          <span class="text-primary/70">DESIGN COM <br/>ESSÊNCIA.</span>
        </h2>
        
        <p class="text-primary/80 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          A RAIZA cria projetos paisagísticos que aliam estética, funcionalidade e sustentabilidade. Cada projeto é único, pensado para valorizar o seu espaço e promover bem-estar.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Image -->
    <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 min-h-[500px] lg:min-h-[600px] relative">
      <img 
        src="/images/about_img.png" 
        alt="Design de paisagismo com piscina e iluminação" 
        class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
